{"type": "article", "id": 35034, "title": "给你一个纸板显微镜，重拾发现的乐趣吧｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-29T23:06:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 35309, "name": "Alias"}, {"id": 35310, "name": "小濑古文库"}, {"id": 35311, "name": "Veronica Szalai"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161130063411ciEOLZpsrWvBte2u.jpeg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>okome by nendo</h3><p>在今年的科隆国际办公家具展上，意大利家具设计公司 <a href=\"http://alias.design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alias</a> 带来了由日本工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 打造的家具系列 Okome。这套有着柔和线条的家具是以被水冲刷的鹅卵石为灵感设计的，四周均为圆角。经由凹陷处它们能够灵活地拼接成一整套沙发组合，适用于办公和居家环境当中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180002Tv0N5w8d7kjegu2t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671149\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611291800031LXr6uYopqkbZAtV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180004xuIXTnsfzoFZY9br.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.304401\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180004TpPnuwUOr603jZmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180004BNT736JXzyGtpq8a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MimeticMaps by Tomoyuki Koseko</h3><p>小濑古文库是一名来自东京的艺术家，对视觉设计有着浓厚的兴趣。这套以常见肉类呈现的 MimeticMaps 地图系列就是他的最新作品，效果也相当惊艳：比如在芬兰地图上，西冷牛排上白色的脂肪就忠实还原了境内的河流。更有趣的是，每张地图海报还贴有逼真的标签，上面详尽地标注了价格和条形码在内的信息。你可以通过<a href=\"https://koseko.stores.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到 A3 大小的海报和画册，售价分别为 1000 和 2000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180020SRN4EVMb2vu1JQxL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180019WM0oXvVzC6ZFBYfp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180019wdJYvHonirqWpL7s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180019mZnQGlDeM1BCNY4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180020cdJ2yUkKtghYqSz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180020s5heDrdog1BZtIwv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Holographic &amp; Matrix by Veronica Szalai</h3><p>把一团纸揉起来就能做成一台挂钟？匈牙利设计师 <a href=\"https://veronikaszalai.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Veronica Szalai</a> 的 NEW TIME 系列把这个听上去不可能的创意变成了现实。这些挂钟的钟面由类似纸张的棉纤维制成，你可以尽情发挥创意把它揉捏成心仪的造型。如果不小心弄脏钟面的话，可以用柔软的海绵擦拭（干湿皆可）。Szalai 为 NEW TIME 设计的包装毫不花哨，只有一个透明的袋子和封装的标签。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/new-time-wall-clock/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些挂钟，售价为 55 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611291800368eZjJHF5wTtPnhaV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180036jDlpeY6tMrq3yzRB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180036L8IuC5EhnepAbRcq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180036KPB5zwYElt1C7cpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180036F28eWBXdtAalsoCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129180036HLnTzwf7tmp3SXOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Frankfurter Brett Basic by Johannes Schreiter &amp; Joseph Schreiter</h3><p class=\"\">在去年成功推出了为大厨设计的模块化砧板 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1461435280/frankfurter-brett-the-kitchen-workbench\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frankfurter Brett</a> 之后，来自德国的 Johannes Schreiter 和 Joseph Schreiter 对其进行了一番针对普通用户的改造，推出了它的 Basic 版。通过在砧板周围加上支架和收纳盒，只要轻轻往旁边刮送，食材和垃圾就能完成归类，让以往混乱的场面变得干净不少。如果你对烹饪还不是很上手，在支架的帮助下，平板电脑或是菜谱也能触手可及。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1461435280/frankfurter-brett-basic-100-grossartig\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 129 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129181728m3eCWqsgLNG5YZJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129181728i4721Jw9KqoBPbDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129181728uIwYLNHn5rDRVMUX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.129412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>TAPS</h3><p class=\"\">随着天气逐渐转冷，不少人都会戴上手套出门，而这也带来了一个新的问题：智能手机感应不到手指无法操作该怎么办？为此来自加拿大的设计团队研发了一款可以被屏幕感应到的双面贴 TAPS，它由军用级别的聚氨酯和纳米粒子材料构成，有着很高的耐用和防水性。设计团队在贴纸表面用 X、Y 轴打造了各不相同的指纹，用户可以直接将 TAPS 的指纹存入设备，这样就能在不摘下手套的情况下完成解锁了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nanotips/taps-touchscreen-sticker-w-touch-id-ships-before-x\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，四个一组的最低价为 15 加元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129182049FygbNqvUtiwGeToa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129182049WxTIXrcOLHoEVF4p.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611291820498JXjMt5CnhiLRomY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.717647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129182049T5xOgY9vq67renSF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Foldscope</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>离开校园之后，似乎没有太多机会可以通过显微镜观察周围的世界。为了让更多人能够以更轻巧便捷的方式理解万物，体验身边的科学乐趣，来自美国的设计团队带来了一款用纸折成的显微镜 Foldscope。显微镜的大部分是由防水的纸板构成的，使用前只要根据折线将它拼装起来即可。除了之前用眼观察之外，手机和投影仪都可以经过它的帮助，让你看到身边的新鲜事物。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/276738145/foldscope-the-origami-paper-microscope\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 20 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129182227pg1LoeljvZPy67uU.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611291822269AO47JPFpIb5diHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161129182226N0rjvK9pH4FwfRqa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.395588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611291822279l6tvXizJbwkVAhW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}